Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.98,0:00:57.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.22,0:01:04.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.23,0:01:10.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.53,0:01:18.56,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.77,0:01:33.05,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.12,0:01:47.56,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.64,0:01:57.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}拉薇練習曲\NEtude Lavie
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要買三級水看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三級水！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以喝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔，給我半加侖的三級水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.96,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹，今晚妳可有口福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我的生日呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我給妳打個折吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好棒的燻肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天保證讓妳肚子飽到睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.02,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個因為熱愛自由的天空\N而下到這片土地來的另類貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從克勞士他家\N搬到我家隔壁後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩家父親很快就結為好友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久便成了一對\N先鋒艇駕駛員及領航員的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和克勞士兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是從一歲的時候起\N就一直在一塊兒長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日\N和媽媽的忌日是同一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在生下我之後\N沒多久就過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉就快烤好了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，這個就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他媽媽\N總是溫柔地在旁看著我和爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，要拍了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.01,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.97,0:04:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒有見過\N我媽媽長什麼樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我家也有照相機的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以留下媽媽的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完成一顆星的任務了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著是下一個任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去媽媽那裡要兩杯冷飲過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險度兩顆星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你囉，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇怎麼在摸魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然接下了任務\N就得把它做完才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家我討厭打掃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的任務讓給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快還我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼式迴轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是用來測克勞地亞的壓力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛行中要目不轉晴的\N好好盯著它看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.79,0:05:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是高度和速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了嗎，再試一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時機一定要抓準才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就能飛了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還真叫人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了那是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一對老是跟著爸爸他們的\N大哥哥大姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要飛越大風暴區！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們能把這封信\N帶給度西斯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以結束這場戰爭\N讓大家過和平的日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼了不起的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然只有爸爸我們\N才能辦得到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一顆，兩顆，三顆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有十顆星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天你也會飛上這片藍天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛得比誰都高，比誰都遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候克勞士你的領航員\N說好就是拉薇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定可以成為\N世界第一的領航員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，很痛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀，抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，媽媽就拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要當心點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，一路順風哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來以後要再讓我坐先鋒艇唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦，是英麥曼式迴轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們最後一次見到爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到爸爸他們死訊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的天空好藍好高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大哥哥獨自一個人\N來傳達這個消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後靜靜地回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我們最後一次\N見到那位大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半年後\N克勞士的媽媽積勞成疾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨他爸爸之後也過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此我們變得舉目無親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.71,0:09:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等將來有一天\N我們一起來飛越它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼式迴轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜沒人在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼他在看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想快一點飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠飛越大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我來當你的領航員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，克勞地亞壓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,節流閥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…我們要飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在飛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.48,0:13:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們賣掉了房子\N保住了爸爸他們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在飛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，在飛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去上邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，這太亂來了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.39,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪可能這麼簡單\N就趕得上爸爸他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧，慢慢來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後我們終於\N連住的地方都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們一點都不以為苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們\N已經可以飛翔在天空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.59,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上只要兩人同心協力\N就沒有什麼做不到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那架飛得太低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是沃卡他兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，都已經到了\N可以接任務的年紀了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，高一點，再高一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你白癡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著是下一個任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險度兩顆星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有十顆星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委託案第11號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險度三顆星，接下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七顆星！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七顆星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看過這樣的任務嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很有魄力不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.93,0:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N反正我還不想死啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為它是我們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你說了是直角嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再搭乘\N戰鬥用的先鋒艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你和我所看的天空\N彼此已經不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你用來戰鬥的先鋒艇\N就讓我來負責照顧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為克勞士你的機械師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有拉薇妳幫我照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就能放心的飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在銀之戰艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，老實說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想留在銀之戰艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和克勞士你一起\N飛在爸爸他們的藍天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛得比誰都高，比誰都遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空原來是這麼的壯觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，感覺好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.44,0:20:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認得出來嗎，是我啦\N莫藍‧謝蘭度啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得那個生還章嗎\N妳親手作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.95,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯的移民艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點鐘方向下方有著陸痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.79,0:21:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，我端熱湯過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.15,0:21:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得在克勞士回來之前\N把爸爸的先鋒艇修好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.39,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡需要一點竅門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，克勞士他回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的城鎮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾齊亞…淪陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.72,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.29,0:22:46.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.19,0:22:51.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.70,0:22:57.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.44,0:23:03.14,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.21,0:23:11.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.02,0:23:17.89,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.96,0:23:23.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.80,0:23:29.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.70,0:23:35.47,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:47.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回預告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.06,0:23:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他人很溫柔\N不過妳別因這件衣服而想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法控制自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜穿著\N克勞士衣服的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直在我腦海揮之不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.70,0:24:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過\N自己竟然是如此脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你人真的很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.21,0:24:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第15話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.05,0:24:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身不由己\NFairy chess
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.08,0:24:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了…蘇菲亞公主
